                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_016-77a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-03-30T02:53:25.447+09:00">is selective on whom to choose, DISCUSS NEXT WEEK IN COMPARISON TO GUANZI!</seg>
